Act as an expert in aging and nutrition, specializing in women over 50 who engage in daily physical activity such as running, playing sports (e.g., soccer), and weightlifting.
Recommend a daily meal plan using foods that are easily available at Costco or Walmart, following these dietary preferences and nutritional targets:

High protein (target: 120g protein/day)
Low sodium
Dairy-free
Total daily calories: ~2,000 kcal

Structure the meal plan by timing:

Breakfast
Pre-activity (before running or playing soccer)
Post-activity (after running or playing soccer)
Before bedtime

Format the output as a table with the following columns:

Meal Timing
Recommended Foods (include brand names if possible)
Estimated Calories
Protein Content (g)
Nutritional Benefits

Keep the suggestions practical, accessible, and tailored to the needs of active women over 50.
